Text: Hey TvTeam, thanks for the uploads, this show is hilarious!  I've downloaded all the other episodes from you and this is the only one I'm having trouble with.  At the very end where the wizard is cutting the "mating bone" off of the demon guy, the audio continues as it should, but the video jumps back to a different scene.  I tried re-downloading and un-raring it again, but it still happens.  Has anyone else that downloaded this experienced this problem?
